final_preprocessed_data_augmentation_35040.py: augment the 70% anomaly ratio dataset in data_anomaly_ratio_handling folder to 35040
data_augmentation_100k.py:augment the 70% anomaly ratio dataset in data_anomaly_ratio_handling folder to 100k

augmented  70%_anomaly_35040data authenticity.py: check whether the augmented 35040 dataset is accurate compared with original dataset
augmented  100k_data authenticity.py:check whether the augmented  100k dataset is accurate compared with original dataset

35040_70%_anomaly_data_x_windows_formed.py： form x_windows for 35040 dataset and use for models' training
100k_data_preparation_x_windows_formed.py: form x_windows for 100k dataset and use for models' training

Deep_AE real1.py,CONV_AE real1.py,LSTM_AE real1.py, CONV_VAE real1.py: 35040 dataset model training
Deep_AE 100k.py,CONV_AE 100k.py,LSTM_AE 100k.py, CONV_VAE 100k.py: 100k dataset model training
